  "name": "nged-connections-reform-register",
  "notes": "The NGED Connection Reform Project Register contains details of all projects submitted by National Grid Electricity Distribution (NGED) as part of the CMP435 process. The register includes only those projects managed directly by NGED and therefore excludes larger projects overseen by the National Energy System Operator (NESO). The dataset provides an inventory of included projects but does not present any outcomes, assessments, or results from the wider reform process.  \r\n\r\n\r\nFor CMP435 outcomes and queue positions please visit Clearview pages: [National Grid - Clearview](https://connections.nationalgrid.co.uk/clear-view/)\r\n",
